
Class Columns (Driver class, imports GameMap)
    methods: run_game

Class GameMap (Gameboard class, imports Faller and all Jewel classes)
    methods: tick, check_match, match, fall, check_events, keydown, draw

Class Faller (Contains 3 random Jewels)
    methods: generate, fall, place, move, check_move, rotate, check_game_over, draw

    Class Jewel
        methods: move, fall, check_fall, draw

        Class BlueJewel [inheritets Jewel]
        Class EmeraldJewel [inheritets Jewel]
        Class GreyJewel [inheritets Jewel]
        Class IndigoJewel [inheritets Jewel]
        Class OrangeJewel [inheritets Jewel]
        Class PinkJewel [inheritets Jewel]
        Class PurpleJewel [inheritets Jewel]
        Class RedJewel [inheritets Jewel]
        Class TealJewel [inheritets Jewel]
        Class YellowJewel [inheritets Jewel]








